  <?dbhtml filename="libpcap.html"?>

  <title>libpcap-&libpcap-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libpcap provides functions for user-level packet capture, used in
      low-level network monitoring.
    </para>

